"tid":1501532,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c33f8b51e2dfa24c4e49c67d11ac368b5f47c763","tid":1501532,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6824323235388c45d097c1ab3f2c320da48a3380","tid":1501532,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94f5daa71e6131af2fecee73d8a438a088ed6d75","tid":1501532,"uid":46824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"去到荃灣公園小心包抄，愉景新城同大窩口都有狗屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">兩邊都去plz </span></strong></span><br />\n跪求無留守意欲嘅手足行完轉車去機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地要長時間塞<br />\n就要keep 住一車車巴士地鐵無間斷流入機場<br />\n<br />\n朝早塞完比人趕返出黎嘅 下午剛好可以遊行<br />\n遊行行到終點就一齊去機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本聽日荃葵青就係天意！<br />\n仲有邊區入機場有咁撚方便？！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRecap:<br />\n<br />\n方案一：<br />\n朝早入機場嘅人下午去遊行<br />\n方案二：<br />\n下午遊行嘅人遊完去機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流水式集會2.0 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入機場原因：<br />\n<br />\n我而家搵到個制衡狗隊濫暴方法<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n[班勇武手足可能一直都去錯地方] 聽朝還眼楂緊政府春袋集會!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"963d247ff1956b75d917f8cb93cd57db3a4f93d2","tid":1501532,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbaa1bd5c28b77ae7e098596b8019a1885e3aad7","tid":1501532,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}